Croogo Sitemap plugin
------------------------------
Creates a XML sitemap for Google


How to use
------------------------------
- Log in to admin panel
- Go to Extensions > Plugins page
- Upload the zip file (available here)
- Click on tick/cross icon of 'Sitemap' for activating or deactivating the plugin


Notes
------------------------------
- Change the default priority for an individual node set CustomField.priority
- Change the default frequency set CustomField.frequency
- Add additional sitemap pages via Extensions > Sitemap > Maintain
- When adding sitemap pages the lastmod is a strtotime field, e.g. enter "-7 days"
- Exclude a node from the sitemap set CustomField.sitemap to false